video.title: The Elephant Princess
video.synopsis: Alexandra Wilson suddenly finds out that she's not an average suburban girl -- she's really the princess of a mystical kingdom!

episodes.synopsis: At Alex's birthday party, an exotic boy and an elephant appear in her backyard. They tell her she is the princess of Manjipoor and that she is magic.
episodes.title: Coming of Age

episodes.synopsis: When Kuru explains Alex has been adopted, she's shocked to find it is true. Upset, she accidentally erases her family from existence.
episodes.title: Don't Call Me Princess

episodes.synopsis: At band auditions, Amanda and J.B. discover Anala -- Alex's elephant. Alex tells them she is a magical princess, but they don't believe her.
episodes.title: Rabbit Season

episodes.synopsis: Kuru enrolls at Alex's school and is a social disaster! To protect him from humiliation, Alex resorts to magic to make him popular.
episodes.title: Kuru the Guru

episodes.synopsis: When Kuru returns to Manjipoor and is trapped by Vashan, Kuru finds he needs to use a magic gift from Alex.
episodes.title: The Powerful Ballad

episodes.synopsis: Infected by Vashan's magic, Alex accidentally creates a new girlfriend for J.B. when she practices her destroy spell.
episodes.title: Not Made in Japan

episodes.synopsis: Alex agrees to visit Manjipoor to meet Omar, but when she realizes it means being a princess, she backs out. As a result, Kuru is fired.
episodes.title: Lean on Me

episodes.synopsis: Amanda convinces Alex to make a trip to Manjipoor, and J.B. travels, too. They arrive in an enchanted forest and meet a family whose son is a mouse!
episodes.title: Welcome to the Fairy Tale

episodes.synopsis: Wanting to know if Marcus is in love with her, Alex does magic and accidentally becomes a frog!
episodes.title: Warts & All

episodes.synopsis: Vashan uses magic to transform Diva into a teenage girl and secretly send her into Alex's world to find out her weaknesses.
episodes.title: The Butterfly Effect

episodes.synopsis: Diva gets closer to Kuru to fracture his close relationship with Alex. She steals the magic runes, and Kuru and Alex have a major argument.
episodes.title: Butterfly Kiss

episodes.synopsis: When Alex discovers that Zoe's only a minor player in her ballet recital, Zoe wants to quit. Unbeknownst to Zoe, Alex lends her magic ballet shoes.
episodes.title: Dancing Queen

episodes.synopsis: Mother's Day makes Alex realize how little she knows about her real mother, Queen Nefari. A visit to Manjipoor leads to a confrontation with her mom!
episodes.title: Destiny's Child

episodes.synopsis: Marcus asks Alex to go on their first date. When things go amiss, she uses "timeslip" magic to reverse time and make every moment of the date perfect.
episodes.title: Time After Time

episodes.synopsis: It's the Royal Elephant Festival in Manjipoor, and Alex will attend as their princess! But things get out of hand when she sneaks her friends in.
episodes.title: Happy Birthday Anala

episodes.synopsis: Marcus and Alex's closeness causes friction in the band when they form a duo to perform in a gig.
episodes.title: The Big Gig

episodes.synopsis: Vashan causes havoc at the school's annual ball and a near-fatal experience for Alex and Marcus when he travels to their world for the first time.
episodes.title: Masquerade Ball

episodes.synopsis: Vashan returns to Alex's world and magically makes her the most famous rock singer on the planet. Alex quickly forgets who she really is.
episodes.title: Almost Too Famous

episodes.synopsis: Amanda goes to Manjipoor and is mistaken by the common people for the princess in disguise. At first, it's not such a bad thing, until Vashan arrives.
episodes.title: Princess Amanda

episodes.synopsis: While making a music video, Marcus feels there is something going on between Alex and Kuru, and secrets the others share except him.
episodes.title: Courtroom Jewel

episodes.synopsis: Alex feels pulled between two worlds when Marcus and Kuru get into a fight over her and Anala goes missing.
episodes.title: Sea Change

episodes.synopsis: Alex decides to commit to being princess of Manjipoor. Vashan ensures the job isn't easy, but Alex is determined.
episodes.title: Revelation

episodes.synopsis: Kuru says his goodbyes -- as Alex is no longer a princess, his job is over. Free of his obligations, he speaks freely of his disappointment in her.
episodes.title: It's an Ordinary Life

episodes.synopsis: Diva makes her move and takes control in Manjipoor, wounding Omar in a fight. Kuru and Anala spirit Omar to Alex's world.
episodes.title: Unexpected Arrivals

episodes.synopsis: Alex studies and uses all her magic to break the barrier between the two worlds to rescue Omar and Anala. It's unprecedented!
episodes.title: Good Vibrations

episodes.synopsis: Her magic stolen by Diva, Alex is regular Alexandra Wilson again. But she leads a rebellion and fights a battle to overthrow Diva.
episodes.title: Normal Alex Wilson
